subSections.text:
{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|屎っ垂れ|くそったれ}}: [[dingleberry]] {{qualifier|vulgar epithet}}
* {{ja-r|目屎|めくそ}}: [[rheum]], [[eye]] [[mucus]]
{{der-bottom}}

{{der-top|Idioms}}
* {{ja-r|屎にする|くそ に する}}: “to turn something into shit; to treat something as shit” → to make something worthless; to treat something as worthless
* {{ja-r|屎の役にも立たぬ|くそ の やく に も たたぬ}}: “not even standing in the role of shit” → not even good for shit
*: (See {{ja-r|役に立つ|やく に たつ}}: “to be useful, to play a role”)
* {{ja-r|屎も味噌も一緒|くそ も みそ も いっしょ}}: “both crap and miso together” → a situation where it is difficult to tell the good from the bad
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-pos|prefix|くそ}}

# {{non-gloss definition|A [[derogatory]] prefix.}}
#: {{ja-usex|'''屎'''爺い|'''くそ'''じじい|'''crappy''' old man}}

{{ja-pos|suffix|くそ}}

# {{non-gloss definition|A [[derogatory]] [[emphasis|emphasizing]] suffix.}}
#: {{ja-usex|下手'''屎'''|へた'''くそ'''|'''crappy''' bad at something; to be '''shit''' at doing something}}
#: {{ja-usex|襤褸'''屎'''|ぼろ'''くそ'''|broken down '''for shit''', raggedy-'''ass'''}}

{{der-top|Idioms}}
* {{ja-r|猫屎する|ねこばばする}}: to [[sweep something under the rug]] → to hide a problem without actually dealing with it {{qualifier|from how a cat will bury its poop}}
{{der-bottom}}
